item.title: One on One Gaming - The 300th: Part One
item.description: Conner is back, and he's the survivor of doomed rearguard against a host of nasty creatures. With the army approaching Conner has to use all his wits to slow down the approaching hoard! Feed: https://feeds.transistor.fm/we-hate-bards-podcasts

item.title: Tour: Embracing a Rejected Star
item.description: Zeta Ophiuchi is a star with a complicated past, having likely been ejected from its birthplace by a powerful stellar explosion. A new look by NASA's Chandra X-ray Observatory helps tell more of the story of this runaway star. Feed: http://chandra.harvard.edu/resources/podcasts/hd/podcasts.xml
